l as future\nsurveys. Finally, as an element of these calculations, we introduce in a\ncosmological setting the Bayesian model dimensionality, which is a\nparameterisation-independent measure of the number of parameters that a given\ndataset constrains.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 11 Feb 2019 18:11:13 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 22 Jul 2019 07:07:24 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 2 Aug 2019 18:01:25 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Thu, 3 Oct 2019 11:41:53 GMT"},{"version":"v5","created":"Sat, 23 Nov 2019 12:20:25 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-11-26"}
