ent direct-detection constraint to\ndate on the WIMP-proton spin-dependent cross section at 2.5 $\\times$ 10$^{-41}$\ncm$^2$ for a 25 GeV WIMP, and improve on previous PICO results for 3-5 GeV\nWIMPs by an order of magnitude.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 11 Feb 2019 18:14:38 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-07-17"}
