 collector is integrated into the\nmaterial, are very different from conventional electrodes and can provide a\nnumber of superior properties.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 11 Feb 2019 20:38:49 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-02-13"}
