ving full diversity order of $\\min(N_A, N_B) \\times\nN_R$ in the MA phase for any modulation order. Monte Carlo simulations are\nprovided which confirm the correctness of the derived analytical results.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 12 Feb 2019 13:46:28 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-02-14"}
